OL,3,CSurvivors 'find peace' 20 years after
OL,4,Cdeadly train crash killed seven
OL,6,FSurvivors of the one of the worst rail
OL,7,Fcrashes in UK history gathered at a
OL,8,Fmemorial garden near the tracks, 20
OL,9,Fyears on from the tragic event.
OL,11,FOn 6 November 2004, seven people died
OL,12,Fand more than 70 were injured in a
OL,13,Frail crash in Ufton Nervet, Berkshire.
OL,15,FA First Great Western train travelling
OL,16,Ffrom London Paddington to Plymouth hit
OL,17,Fa car which had parked across the
OL,18,Ftracks on the line between Theale and
OL,19,FNewbury.
