OL,3,CSurvivors 'find peace' 20 years after
OL,4,Cdeadly train crash killed seven
OL,6,FIn 2016, the level crossing where the
OL,7,Fcrash took place, was replaced with a
OL,8,Fbridge as part of an #8m project,
OL,9,Fwhich survivors had been campaigning
OL,10,Ffor.
OL,12,FThe 17:35 service was almost 40 mins
OL,13,Finto its journey when Brian Drysdale
OL,14,Fdrove onto the tracks at Ufton Nervet
OL,15,Fand parked his car in its path.
OL,17,FInitially the train stayed upright,
OL,18,Fbut as it moved up the tracks it hit
OL,19,Fthe points and all eight carriages
OL,20,Fwere derailed.
