OL,3,CSurvivors 'find peace' 20 years after
OL,4,Cdeadly train crash killed seven
OL,6,FThe lights on the train went out and
OL,7,Fpassengers on board described how it
OL,8,Ffelt like being in a tumble dryer
OL,9,Fbefore everything stopped.
OL,11,FEmergency services were on the scene
OL,12,Fwithin minutes of receiving dozens of
OL,13,F999 calls. It was later revealed that
OL,14,Fnearby fireworks displays helped them
OL,15,Fsee in the pitch black.
