OL,3,CSurvivors 'find peace' 20 years after
OL,4,Cdeadly train crash killed seven
OL,6,FAt the time of the crash, the level
OL,7,Fcrossing was controlled by half
OL,8,Fbarriers. It would be more than ten
OL,9,Fyears, following intense campaigning,
OL,10,Fbefore a bridge was built over the
OL,11,Frailway lines to separate road and
OL,12,Frail traffic.
OL,14,FSurvivors say the bridge has helped
OL,15,Fthem find peace.
