OL,3,CSurvivors 'find peace' 20 years after
OL,4,Cdeadly train crash killed seven
OL,6,FOne of the survivors, Julie Lloyd
OL,7,Fsaid: "After that night this area
OL,8,Fbecame a no-go area, it was
OL,9,Ffrightening, it was horrible but over
OL,10,Fthe years it's gone back to the
OL,11,Fpeaceful area it actually is, I've
OL,12,Fmanaged to get that back again now.
OL,14,F"The bridge has waylaid the fact that
OL,15,F- it can't happen again, not here
OL,16,Fanyhow, which has made a great deal of
OL,17,Fdifference.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
