OL,3,CSurvivors 'find peace' 20 years after
OL,4,Cdeadly train crash killed seven
OL,6,F"It is a shared experience. There's
OL,7,Fgoing to be a lot of people here, I
OL,8,Fcan imagine, for the first time. I
OL,9,Fhope they get the sense of
OL,10,Fpeacefulness that most of us have now
OL,11,Fgot.
OL,13,F"Those of us who come regularly every
OL,14,Fyear know why we're there. We talk
OL,15,Famongst ourselves. There's no
OL,16,Fformality, no standing on ceremony.
OL,18,F"We either share stories or we don't.
OL,19,FWe cry together or laugh together, and
OL,20,Fit's peaceful. It's been healing for a
OL,21,Flot of us."
